e rods; and offers hydraulic fittings, fluid connectors, flanges, valves, and couplings. In addition, it engages in the business of international and domestic trading, investment and finance, leasing of assets, and manufacture and sale of flexible packaging, as well as provides engineering, aftermarket, and replacement services; and equivalent compressor spare parts. It serves agro pesticides, basic drug, cattle feed, cement, and other industries. The company was formerly known as Sat Industries Limited and changed its name to Aeroflex Enterprises Limited in May 2025. Aeroflex Enterprises Limited was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}